==Results== ===[[Spanish general election, 2008|2008 General Election]]=== The PSOE obtained their best ever result in the district in 2008, polling an absolute majority for the first time. This had last been achieved by the UCD in the 1979 election. The city of León itself produced a result close to the district average with the PSOE polling 48.3% against 44.4% for the PP. In Ponferrada, PSOE led PP by 51.2% to 42.3%
